  <brief_title>Effect of Liraglutide on Blood Glucose Control in Japanese Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Liraglutide on Glycaemic Control in Japanese Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes.</official_title>
